N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4223.10 - Official program

State Regulations

The racing secretary shall publish on the official
program such information and notices to the public as the commission may
direct; and shall be responsible for any error of commission or omission in the
official program for each racing day. Notes
